OL,3,CStormont draft budget to be announced
OL,4,Cin December
OL,6,FStormont's draft budget is set to be
OL,7,Fannounced next month, the finance
OL,8,Fminister has indicated.
OL,10,FCaoimhe Archibald said following last
OL,11,Fweek's Budget announcement by
OL,12,FChancellor Rachel Reeves, it is her
OL,13,Fintention to publish Northern
OL,14,FIreland's budget in December.
