OL,3,CStormont draft budget to be announced
OL,4,Cin December
OL,6,FSpeaking during question time for her
OL,7,Fdepartment in the Assembly, Ms
OL,8,FArchibald said that timing would allow
OL,9,Ffor a full 12-week consultation before
OL,10,Fa final budget is agreed by the
OL,11,FExecutive ahead of the start of the
OL,12,Fnext financial year.
OL,14,FShe said it will be a one year budget
OL,15,Fbecause the Chancellor's statement
OL,16,Fonly covered 2025/26, but that moving
OL,17,Fforward she intends to move to multi-
OL,18,Fyear budgets where multi-year spending
OL,19,Freview settlements allow.
