OL,6,FMs Archibald also told MLAs that she
OL,7,Fhas brought proposals to the Executive
OL,8,Fin relation to the region's rating
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,FShe said it is important that the
OL,12,Frating system is as "fair, progressive
OL,13,Fand equitable as possible", and
OL,14,F"aligns with what we're trying to
OL,15,Fachieve economically and socially".
OL,17,FShe referred to creating an
OL,18,Fenvironment which "supports businesses
OL,19,Fto start up, to thrive, to create
OL,20,Fjobs".
