OL,6,F"I am committed to working across the
OL,7,FExecutive and with business
OL,8,Forganisations and others across
OL,9,Fsociety to ensure that we have the
OL,10,Fbest system possible and that any rate
OL,11,Frelief that we have in place are
OL,12,Fensuring that they continue to meet
OL,13,Fthe policy objectives that they were
OL,14,Fput in place to do," she said.
OL,16,FThe minister added: "I had hoped by
OL,17,Fnow that I would have secured
OL,18,FExecutive agreement to my proposals,
OL,19,Fand as a result, would have been in a
OL,20,Fposition to update the House on the
OL,21,Fway forward.
