OL,6,F"Every pound that we are spending on
OL,7,Frate relief means reduced revenue for
OL,8,Fpublic services or higher rates bills
OL,9,Ffor other homes and businesses and in
OL,10,Fthat context, we must make sure every
OL,11,Frate support measure is achieved in
OL,12,Fthe desired policy outcome and is
OL,13,Fdelivering for citizens and businesses.
